btw after installing db2 client stuff and running the new db2profile comand it still didnt work (cpan DBD::DB2) 
11:08:28 PM: iandallas@uk.ibm.com - Ian Dallas/UK/IBM: so i had to copy the *.h files from the include folder created by DSDriver:  
11:08:29 PM: iandallas@uk.ibm.com - Ian Dallas/UK/IBM: sqlca.h    sqlcli.h  sqlenv.h  sql.h       sqlsystm.h
sqlcli1.h  sqlda.h   sqlext.h  sqlstate.h
 
into db2 include folder /opt/ibm/db2/V10.1/include 
then cpan DBD::DB2 worked 
